Title: Relates to the establishment of a developmental disability clinician advisory group by the commissioner of health
Summary: Relates to the establishment of a developmental disability clinician advisory group by the commissioner of health.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend part C of chapter 60 of the laws of 2014, amending the social services law and other laws relating to eliminating prescriber prevails for brand name drugs with generic equivalents, in relation to the establishment of a developmental disability clinician advisory group by the commissioner of health
